{"sequence":17,"timestamp":"2026-04-07T05:54:24.826283816Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-55ffd426","body":"The analogous function `resolve_prompt_review_panel_for_preflight` (engine.rs:352-371) has the exact same bug pattern that was just fixed for final_review: it resolves `refiner` via generic `resolve_role_target(BackendPolicyRole::PromptReviewer, cycle)` then overwrites `panel.refiner` returned by `resolve_prompt_review_panel()`, which already correctly checks `prompt_review_policy().refiner_backend` for a dedicated override. If `prompt_review.refiner_backend` is configured, the preflight silently ignores it. Apply the same delegation pattern: replace the body with a direct call to `policy.resolve_prompt_review_panel(cycle).map_err(...)` to avoid the override bypass.","dedup_key":"5f8c7022e05b487965bf20a3a88d9cce93e5a65fa35ca3e842844443e9024f86","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"claude","model_id":"claude-opus-4-6","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260407053506","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":18,"timestamp":"2026-04-07T05:54:24.835632625Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-b1f75686","body":"src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:381-385 regresses preflight inspectability by collapsing every final-review resolution error into a generic \"final-review panel resolution failed\" message. That strips the failing member identity for planner/arbiter/reviewer failures; the existing feature-gated assertion at tests/unit/workflow_engine_test.rs:2060-2064 now fails because a planner resolution error no longer mentions \"planner\". Keep the dedicated final_review planner/arbiter resolution path, but preserve member-specific wrapping (or otherwise propagate the exact failing target/config source) so preflight failures still identify which final-review member failed.","dedup_key":"da7fc96b5f392d98bf8000745832a8e3fa2447d47c8cc854ad2af3fdd464878d","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4","reviewer_id":"reviewer-2"}],"run_id":"run-20260407053506","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
